{title: H364 - Día en Día}
{subtitle: Day by Day (and with each passing moment)}
{author: Carolina (Lina) Sandell-Berg (1865)}
{ccli: 104479}
{key: E}
{tempo: 78}
{time: 4/4}
{duration: 2:42}
